features: [Maximize Corner Space] Standing at 16.7”D x 15.5”W x 65.4”H, this tall corner cabinet makes full use of the spare corner space to offer plenty of vertical storage while taking up little floor space, perfect for small spaces
[4 Adjustable Shelves] 2 adjustable shelves behind each door allow you to set them at 3 different heights, fitting either tall or short items while keeping them hidden from view

[Fits Various Rooms] Able to slide perfectly against any corner, this storage cabinet works well in various spaces—for toiletries in the bathroom, dinnerware in the kitchen, or table cloths in the dining room
[Hidden Anti-Tip Kit] The anti-tip kit, hidden from view, not only prevents the cupboard from toppling but also ensures that there’s no presence of ugly hardware from the outside

[Modern Farmhouse Charm] With a geometric profile and slat doors adorned with silver, diamond-shaped handles, this cabinet effortlessly brings a modern farmhouse design for that cozy, feel-good atmosphere

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful and sturdy
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I put together myself took about 2hours because first part stumped me. It was a loose base but once you screwed to flat piece was very sturdy. Rest of pieces was breeze to put together. It cam out beautiful it is heavy and has anchor screws as well for the wall. I wanted extra space on my bathroom counter and to draw your eye up this was perfect. I will be changing light fixture so it fits better. But overall great buy for the money.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for my esparce!
reviews.reviewText: Just as described in website, good quality, nice looking & perfect for a corner space. Like it very much!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good cabinet but?
reviews.reviewText: We like the cabinet easy to assemble and fits great but has a Chemical smell to it, pretty strong hoping it goes away if not then it goes back but that’s the only reason we didn’t give it a 5 star. Update after a couple days the smell seems to be going away.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Finally a good corner cabinet
reviews.reviewText: This worked out perfectly as a linen cabinet in my laundry room. Not huge but good enough for a small household. Easy enough to put together and sturdy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 15, 2022
reviews.reviewText: We needed something for an odd corner in our kitchen and this was perfect. It isn't as sturdy as we would like but it works. Good price - like an Ikea product as far as instructions go but it wasn't difficult to assemble. I would recommend this product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Holes not drilled through. Missing parts. No written directions.
reviews.reviewText: This is the first time I have completely given up and had to return assemble it yourself furniture. This was a mess. The holes were not drilled all the way through. The existing holes had debris build up in them and it was missing two parts. Also, the directions were not in written out just pictures.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for Corners inside Bathrooms
reviews.reviewText: Perfect for my purpose, small Bathroom and now with a lot of space for storage.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Fit perfect in the corner....
reviews.reviewText: We had been searching for a corner cabinet for a while. This one fit perfect in the space we needed. I gave 4 stars because one of the panels came damaged with a small crack in the corner. It was not worth trying to replace so I put it together as is. Directions were not the greatest, but just take your time and it goes together pretty easy. I had all parts needed and all holes where they needed to be. So far it has been working out great.
